---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
		<div class="mb-16">
			<h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
				Consulting & Advisory Services
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 sm:text-xl">
				I help organizations and leaders build systems that scale opportunity. Whether you need to transform how you use data, navigate strategic change, secure funding, or build high-performance teams, I bring evidence-based approaches and hands-on execution.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-16 space-y-12">
			<section class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-12">
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">
					Data & Analytics
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
					Transform raw data into actionable insights. I help organizations build analytics capacity, design evaluation frameworks, and use evidence to drive decision-making. From survey design and validation to longitudinal analysis and causal inference, I bring rigorous methods to complex problems.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Data architecture and analytics infrastructure</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Program evaluation and impact measurement</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Survey design and validation studies</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>RCT design and causal inference methods</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Strategic reporting and data visualization</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-12">
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">
					Organizational Strategy & Change Management
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
					Navigate complex transitions with clarity and purpose. I help leaders design strategic plans, manage digital transformations, and build the capacity needed to execute ambitious goals. My approach combines data-driven strategy with servant leadership principles.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Strategic planning and goal-setting frameworks</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Digital transformation and technology selection</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Change management and stakeholder alignment</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Partnership development and relationship management</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Financial modeling and strategic finance</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-12">
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">
					Grant Writing & Development
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
					Secure funding with compelling narratives backed by evidence. I help organizations craft grant proposals that tell a clear story, demonstrate impact, and align with funder priorities. My background in policy research and program evaluation means proposals are grounded in rigorous evidence.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Grant proposal writing and editing</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Logic model and theory of change development</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Impact measurement and evaluation design</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Funder research and alignment strategies</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Budget development and financial narratives</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-12">
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">
					Fitness & Performance Coaching
				</h2>
				<p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
					Build discipline and capacity that compounds. As a Certified CrossFit Trainer (CF-L3), I help individuals and teams develop the consistency, standards, and mental resilience needed to achieve ambitious goals. The same principles that drive organizational success apply to physical performance.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Individual coaching and program design</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Team training and group fitness programming</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Movement analysis and technique refinement</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="mr-2 mt-1.5 text-primary">→</span>
						<span>Performance mindset and goal-setting</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</div>

		<section class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-8 sm:p-12">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">
				Get In Touch
			</h2>
			<p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
				Interested in working together? I take on a limited number of consulting engagements each year, focusing on projects where I can make meaningful impact. Let's discuss how I can help you achieve your goals.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
				<a
					href="mailto:pmagouir@gmail.com"
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-neutral-900 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:bg-neutral-800 hover:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900 focus:ring-offset-2"
				>
					Email Me
				</a>
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/preston-magouirk-840aa757/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-neutral-200 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors hover:border-neutral-900 hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neutral-900 focus:ring-offset-2"
				>
					Connect on LinkedIn
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
